  "body": "### Description\n\nSuppose we have this very simple class as a Mongo entity with a custom `String` as an `id`\r\n ```\r\n @MongoEntity\r\npublic class Person {\r\n\r\n    private String id;\r\n    private String name;\r\n\r\n    // constructors & getters & setters \r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen querying we have to use `_id` as it is stored in Mongo like:\r\n`find(\"_id\", id)` when it should make sense to use `find(\"id\", id)`\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
